text: Mischarytera macrobotrys is a species of rainforest trees, of the flowering plant family Sapindaceae. They grow naturally in Cape York Peninsula, Queensland, Australia and Papua New Guinea. ==References== ==External links== * Category:Sapindaceae Category:Sapindales of Australia Category:Flora of Papua New Guinea Category:Least concern flora of Australia Category:Flora of Queensland Category:Least concern biota of Queensland Category:Taxonomy articles created by Polbot
